# FORT-6 (P2 Codex audit): env files MUST stay out of git. Previously
# only *.local was ignored, so .env / .env.development / .env.production
# leaked into the repo (and into history). If you need a template for
# new devs, commit `.env.example` with placeholder values — it's the
# only env-shaped file allowed.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

